 change.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aAustronesian languagesxGrammar. 0aAustronesian languagesxMorphology. 0aAustronesian languagesxSyntax. 4aAustronesische Sprachen. 4aSyntax. 4aTypologie /Sprachen. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aOceanic/Austronesian Languages.  aSyntax.  aTypology.1 aBril, Isabelle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIkiua, Ofania, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMargetts, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMassam, Diane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoyse-Faurie, Claire, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoyse-Faurie, Claire, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOtsuka, Yuko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPearce, Elizabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPolinsky, Maria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPotsdam, Eric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSabel, Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSabel, Joachim, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStarks, Donna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVernaudon, Jacques, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 20